  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Print Templates allow you to choose which information appears on invoices and receipts. Certain information may be required on these documents for companies subject to GST/VAT or similar tax laws. This article will guide you through updating these details in RepairQ to ensure they are visible to your customers.</p><p>In the examples below, we'll focus on GST-friendly labeling. However, you can customize the names of these fields according to your preferences. Please note that these changes are purely visual and will not affect the pricing calculations.</p><h3 id=\"Tax-inclusivePricing:GSTInvoiceTemplate-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1986035723\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing: Customize Ticket Display</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2713288722\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing: GST Receipt Template</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1933410332\" rel=\"nofollow\">Setting up and Assigning Tax Rates</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1984823420\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-Inclusive Pricing: Company and Location Setup</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1986560223\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-Inclusive Pricing Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/kb/view/1932394639\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing on Tickets</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560182/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Tax-inclusivePricing:GSTInvoiceTemplate-IncludeTaxIDandTax-InclusiveInfoonInvoices\">Include Tax ID and Tax-Inclusive Info on Invoices</h2><p>On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Settings </strong>\u2192 <strong>Location Settings</strong>. On the Settings Overview page, under the Templates category, click <strong>Invoices</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560182/GST%20ReceiptsInvoice%201.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560182/GST%20ReceiptsInvoice%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>On the <strong>Invoice Template</strong> page, you can customize which details will be printed on your invoices. Use your discretion to include relevant fields that best suit your needs. For this demonstration, we will focus on highlighting GST-specific fields. Once you\u2019ve made your customizations, don't forget to click <strong>Save</strong> to apply your changes.</p><h3 id=\"Tax-inclusivePricing:GSTInvoiceTemplate-InvoiceSettings\">Invoice Settings</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560182/GST%20ReceiptsInvoice%203.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Invoice Title </strong>- Assign a title for your invoice that will be visible when printing.</p><ul><li><p>For GST customers, you can name this as 'Tax Invoice.'</p></li></ul></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560182/GST%20ReceiptsInvoice%205.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Ticket Items </strong>- Select this option to include a line detail for ticket items.</p></li><li><p><strong>Line Item Price/Tax Display</strong> - Select how line item prices and taxes appear on the invoice.</p><ul><li><p>For GST Customers, we recommend selecting <strong>Tax-inclusive: show tax-inclusive price, effective after-tax discount, etc</strong>.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Tax-Inclusive Unit Price (Before Discount)</strong> - This includes the price of all items on the ticket before discounts are applied.</p><ul><li><p>For GST, we recommend using \u2018Subtotal (Inc GST).\u2019</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Effective AFter-tax Discount</strong> - The total of any discounts applied toward ticket items.</p><ul><li><p>For GST, we recommend using \u2018Discount (Inc GST).\u2019</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Tax </strong>- This is the total for all taxes applied to the ticket items.</p><ul><li><p>For GST, we recommend using \u2018GST.\u2019</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id=\"Tax-inclusivePricing:GSTInvoiceTemplate-TicketTotals\">Ticket Totals</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560182/GST%20ReceiptsInvoice%206.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Tax-Inclusive Ticket Total Without Discounts</strong> - This includes the price of all items on the ticket before discounts are applied.</p><ul><li><p>For GST, we recommend using \u2018Subtotal (Inc GST).\u2019</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Total Effective After-Tax Discount</strong> - The total of any discounts applied toward ticket items.</p><ul><li><p>For GST, we recommend using 'Discount (Inc GST).'</p></li></ul></li></ul><hr/><h2 id=\"Tax-inclusivePricing:GSTInvoiceTemplate-ViewinganInvoiceAfterCustomization\">Viewing an Invoice After Customization</h2><p>After saving your template, you can print an invoice from the <strong>Ticket View</strong> page. The fields will be updated to reflect your recent changes.</p><p>This example demonstrates how the column names and labels appear after updating the invoice template:</p><ul><li><p>Invoice Settings</p><ul><li><p><strong>Invoice Title</strong> - Invoice \u2192 Tax Invoice</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Ticket Items</p><ul><li><p><strong>Tax-Inclusive Unit Price (Before Discount)</strong> - Price \u2192 (Inc GST)</p></li><li><p><strong>Effective AFter-tax Discount</strong> - Discount \u2192 Discount (Inc GST)</p></li><li><p><strong>Tax </strong>- Tax \u2192 GST</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Ticket Totals</p><ul><li><p><strong>Tax-Inclusive Ticket Total Without Discounts</strong> - Subtotal \u2192  Subtotal (Inc GST)</p></li><li><p><strong>Total Effective After-Tax Discount </strong>- Discount \u2192 Discount (Inc GST)</p></li></ul></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"GST ReceiptsInvoice 7.png\" width=\"596\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560182/GST%20ReceiptsInvoice%207.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
